text:
chalo atleat tune to profile bnayi. Sid, B Bot ka stud and cool londa. bhai tere jaisa cool or relaxed banda nhi dekha apne college m.agar kisi ko college  chaapna ho to tumse sikhe..har jagah next level chaap rkha h. m to bc yhi sochta rhta tu y sab karte hue (ifywim) bhi tu itna kaise chap leta tha.
Apna itna interaction to nhi hua (kyoki tu rahta hi nhi tha wing m) par chill h apan to bagal m hi milte rhenge.
Enjoy your life and wish you lot of success. milenge jald hi. Byeeee
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text: Aur be PP !!! vo 1st year ki summer k kya hi din the bc. puri raat us ek hi bed p bethke k pubg khelna or subah phir doaa canteen m breakfast karna. alag hi bakchod din the bc. baaki jab bhi tera naam yaad aata h to teri vo "Laura'' vala accent yaad aata h. baki enjoy kar or chapta rah. Hopefully milthe h kabhi.
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text: Helloo sirrrr...aap to alag hi chaapu ho!! mangal ki maarna aapne hi chalu kri thi first year m or chalta hi rha.First year ki bakchodi alag hi level ki thi...vo bhi kya din the. Baki sir ese hi chapte rho or enjoy kro...hopefully milte h jald hi byye.
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text: Hi Parshad ! we met during esc201 lab. my lab was too easy with you as lab partner and enjoyed a lot. hopefully we will meet in future till then enjoy your life. all the best. byee
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text: hi Shashank bhai...apni mulakat to sabse pahle shubham ke through hi hui thi. jab first year m shubham k room m mahfil lagti thi, alag hi bakchodi kri thi. uske baad phatta khela sath m, tere shots bhi bakchod hote the or jab lagatar harte the to tereko gussa bhi bahut aata tha. Vo lucknow m match ka experience bhi acha. baki ho to tum chapu hi..ese hi chapte rho or enjoy karoo.hopefully milte h kabhi ! byeee
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text:
bore ho rah tha to socha aaj likh hi deta hu....
jab sabse pahle mila tha to ekdum sharif insaan tha( mangal se bhi shareef , y to bezzati ho gyi bc haha) gali vali kuch nhi deta tha. phir dhire dhire launde ka biharipan bahar aane hi lga or ban gya ekdam bakait. Yaad h jab apan CPA m jaate the or apni alag drills or trainings hockey sikhne k liye. enthu to tha pta nhi kyo sikh nhi paaye. 
Mangal ki milkar marne ka alag hi mjaa tha bc or vo jab uski fb ka password hack kiya tha alag hi mja aaya tha. vo CCD vala kand jo mere p hi ulta pad gya tha or mene bc usko dil p le liya (lol kitna chutiya tha me bhi). 
Afsos rhega apan last m mil nhi paye last m ( tere chutiyape ki vajah) par chill mar jald hi milenge or milte rhenge. 
till then all the best for your future life and wish you a lot of success.
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text:
motiiiiii....y londa alag hi chapu h
1st year m to apna itna interaction nhi( ab tum the hi itne chapuuuu) tha kyoki tu khi or hi busy rhta tha( iywim). 251 k baad apni baatchit chalu hui thi. bss teri or tanmay ki kripa s chemical ki degree complete ho paayii. 
vo D-mid ki bakchodi hmesha hi yaar rhegi, raat ko canteen jana(na mann hone aor bhi) or class k baad  tumhare sath MT jana, or vo vala kaand hmesha hi yaad rhega. 
 yhi khushi thegi ki apan last baar mil paye .last month to kabhi nhi bhul sakta, vo hall 13 ki canteen jana, patte khelna or maggi bnana( jo bc kabhi nhi kiya 4 saal m). 
wishing a lot of success and happiness in your life and milenge jald hi.
till then alvida
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar

text:
hmare wing repi, chacha ( " m tere s baat nhi krunga aaage s mereko chacha bola tha..lol) jisne bhi tereko wing repi bnaya ekdam shi kiya. har kaam m sabko sath leke chalta tha.  hall 2 m vo phatta khelna hmesha hi yaad rhega, tere lambe lambe shot ( "yaar chhat p jane k 8 run kro"), overconfidence m aake aadhi crease p jake khelna or miss ho jana hahaha, or pta nhi bich m konsha josh aa jata tha bowling krne aa jata tha or wide p wide, or H2PL m hagna, D-mid m phatta khelna. 
mse ki class m late jana or quiz m cheating ...kya hi bakchod din the yar vo. apni trip bhi hamesha yaad rhegi ..kese log pighal jaate h ( photos padi h mere pass, leak to karni padegi ).
Last k ek mahine ki bakchodi bhi alag hi level ki thi bsss jab tu bich m khel chhodke bhaag jata tha or sab chale jate the to bahut gussa aata tha tere p.hahaha.
Chill h apan to jald hi mil rhe h noida m or ab sath hi rahna h to ese hi bakchodi hoti rhegi. tab tak tu paise chhapta rah and be happy.
milte h jald hi byee
author: Rahul Kumar Khichar
